Yeah!
對！

5
00:02:49,291 --> 00:02:50,916
Yes, it's close.
恩，很接近了

6
00:02:50,916 --> 00:02:52,666
How close?
有多近了？

7
00:02:52,666 --> 00:02:55,708
Well, can't you feel the heat?
恩，你們沒有感覺到那熱氣嗎？

8
00:03:14,833 --> 00:03:19,125
So that the sky might turn blue
那天空可能會變藍

9
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:24,291
So that the planet might be one
而那星球也將成為其中之一

10
00:03:25,083 --> 00:03:27,083
And mankind...
而人類…

11
00:03:34,833 --> 00:03:37,416
See how he likes that? 
Can't you see?
你們看他有多喜歡？
看不出來嗎？

12
00:03:37,416 --> 00:03:39,791
He's really enjoying it.
他真的很享受

13
00:03:40,291 --> 00:03:42,083
- It's me?
- No.
我的？
不是

14
00:03:44,291 --> 00:03:45,166
Hey...
嘿…

15
00:03:45,625 --> 00:03:48,750
...take that stuff off my face, damn it! Shit!
把那東西從我臉上移開，該死的！媽的！

16
00:04:56,458 --> 00:04:58,416
Asshole!
混蛋！

17
00:05:22,375 --> 00:05:23,875
Attention everyone!
各位注意一下！

18
00:05:23,875 --> 00:05:26,416
Lunch is served!
中餐可以開始享用了！

19
00:05:28,125 --> 00:05:31,208
Hey, get to the back of the line!
嘿，到後面排隊去！

20
00:05:32,375 --> 00:05:34,583
What if you meet someone?
要是你遇見了甚麼人呢？

21
00:05:34,583 --> 00:05:38,000
- We never know.
- Yes, it's better to be prepared.
世事難料
對呀，最好先有心理準備

22
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,541
- Have a nice meal.
- Thanks.
祝你用餐愉快
謝謝

23
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:48,166
- Come here, get in. Come on!
- Thanks.
來呀，排這。來嘛！
謝了

24
00:05:48,166 --> 00:05:51,416
After all, you're growing up girl.
畢竟，妳也在發育嘛

25
00:11:01,708 --> 00:11:08,250
I wouldn't miss you at all
on a sunny sunday at Beach Park
我一點都不會想你
在 海灘公園 一個晴朗的星期天

26
00:11:08,250 --> 00:11:15,041
There's no way I would take you along
for a walk with me at Iguatemi Mall.
我是不可能帶你一起逛Iguatemi商場

27
00:11:15,041 --> 00:11:22,041
I wouldn't dare facing the embarrassment
in front of my cool friends from Aldeota.
我無法面對被那些自Aldeota朋友發現的窘境

28
00:11:22,041 --> 00:11:29,833
Because now I hold a high reputation
among the high circles of high society.
因為我在現在的社交圈裡有一定的地位

29
00:11:29,833 --> 00:11:37,083
I know that the bourgeoisie stinks
but it has money to buy perfume.
雖然我知道那資產階級的腐敗但那讓我有錢得到我要的

30
00:11:37,083 --> 00:11:43,583
What's more, in the high society
people are cheated on without getting jealous.
再者，在這資本社會裡人們毫無理由的互相欺騙

31
